VOLUMES:
-----------
why we have use volumes?
if in realtime you data will store in container if container was deleted your data will also deleted
to retrive that issue volumes is best option

4 types off volumes
---------------------
1->Empty volume->these volume will create in side the pod if pod was deleted the data also will be deleted
2->HostVolume-> it will stored in nodes if pods deteleted data will stored in node..if incase node will be deleted data also will be delete
3->PV and PVC ->it will store is cloud like AWS EBS->if node deleted or pod deleted you data will be safe(realtime we will use these)

