Resource Quata:
----------------
what is resource?
it is nothing like ram,cpu,memory
Why resource quote?
whem you run pod or container in server you didint mention resource all limit will be taken by first conatiner
if is runs like these you can phase some problems with another container.

Advantages of these?
1.node have 4cpu 8gb ram
1 micro serive have less traffic another 2 micro service have high traffic on that time
i will give 1 cpu 3gb ram for micro ser-1 and 3 cpu 5gb ram for micro-sev-2

first we have to attach Resource Quoata for namespace then we have to use
apiVersion: v1
kind: ResourceQuota
metadata:
  name: myreq
  namespace: dev
spec:
  hard:
    limits.cpu: "500m"
    requests.cpu: "250m"
    limits.memory: "100Mi"    # Changed: Mi (Mebibytes)
    requests.memory: "50Mi"    # Changed: Mi (Mebibytes)
-------------------------------------------------
Note : onec you attached these resource quote you have to mention resources for pod or deployment creation
if not not enterd it will get error
